. (A) Hydrotheca, lateral view; (B) portion of a colony; (C) hydrothecal diaphragm; (D) base of hydrotheca showing desmocytes; (E) gonothecae, lateral view. Scale bars: 200 Mm (A); 1.0 mm (B); 25 Mm (C); 100 Mm (D); 500 Mm (E).
</paragraph>
